            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1679660035302-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are fork-tender, mash them until smooth</p><p>Break up the <strong>crab meat</strong> gently with a fork, then add it to the crushed potatoes with the <strong>ground paprika</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix it all together – this is your<strong> crab cake mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1679660039315-x200.jpg",
