    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Wash the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the<strong> cucumber<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> and <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
