      "instruction": "<p>Bring a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Crack the <strong>eggs</strong> gently into the <strong>water</strong> and leave them for 3 min</p><p>Once done, gently transfer the <strong>eggs </strong>with a slotted spoon to kitchen paper or a clean tea-towel and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – these are your <strong>poached eggs</strong></p>",
